                        Add Review
                    </h3>
                    <div class="padding-top-10px">
                        <form>
                            <div class="form-row">
                                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                                    <label for="inputName">Full Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputName4" placeholder="Name">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
